inor/major expansion and deployment support. Further, it provides software design and development; electronic media; IT and media training; consulting and mobile app development; and software testing services for web and desktop applications, mobile apps, and data warehouses. Additionally, the company operates JAN TV, a satellite TV channel that provides education, news, employment, skill development, agriculture, tourism, healthcare, religious, sports, entertainment, and current affairs-based programs. Compucom Software Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Jaipur, India."}}